==Merged second translation== {{Infobox East Asian name |title=Munefuda |img=Munefuda.jpg |imgwidth=200px |caption=Munefuda at {{ill|Nagashima Waterside Serenity Park|ja|長島水辺のやすらぎパーク|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Nagashima Waterside Serenity Park|qq=}}, showing the inscription from Meiji 12 (1879).
