{{Infobox East Asian name |title=Munafuda |img=Munefuda.jpg |imgwidth=200px |caption=A {{ill|Munafuda|ja|棟札|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Munafuda|qq=}} from the {{ill|Kuga Residence|ja|長島水辺のやすらぎパーク|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kuga Residence|qq=}}, showing the year Meiji 12 (1879).
